{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>学校在最近几天有$n$个活动，这些活动都需要使用学校的大礼堂，在同一时间，礼堂只能被一个活动使用。由于有些活动时间上有冲突，学校办公室人员只好让一些活动放弃使用礼堂而使用其他教室。<p><p>现在给出$n$个活动使用礼堂的起始时间$begin\\_i$和结束时间$end\\_i(begin\\_i < end\\_i)$，请你帮助办公室人员安排一些活动来使用礼堂，要求安排的活动尽量多。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"活动选择 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出最多能安排的活动个数。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行一个整数$n(n≤1000)$；<p><p>接下来的$n$行，每行两个整数，第一个$begin\\_i$，第二个是$end\\_i(begin\\_i< end\\_i ≤32767)$。<p>","examples":"<input>11\n3 5\n1 4\n12 14\n8 12\n0 6\n8 11\n6 10\n5 7\n3 8\n5 9\n2 13\n</input><output>4\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1323","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}